I kinda have no words 🥹 Jordan was literally perfection last night! 

This full @off____white look (boots too) that Jordan wore to the @thetonyawards was absolutely God sent! If you’ve seen his play @aintnomobway, you know that it’s about what if all Black people were offered a plane ticket to move to Africa to combat a lot of the social injustices we face in the United States. The suit has groups of people painted on the leather that look like they’re either walking towards or away from something (some are even running) and when I saw it my initial thought was holy shit, they’re  walking to the plane they’re walking to the FUKN plane 🤯 I immediately got chills, and knew this was the suit we had to have. If you’ve ever heard Jordan give a speech about @aintnomobway he ends every speech with enjoy your flight so clearly we had to have a custom airplane necklace to complete the look. I called my good Judy @kalihawk and asked her if she could make a custom @h.crowne airplane necklace and she came all the way through, in less than a week 🙌🏾✈️. And for the icing on the cake I arrange for @ebonymagazine to film a GRWM with @jordanecooper because this look and his story DESERVE (I can’t wait to post it) Damn, when I read all this back, I really did my big one 🙌🏾 

Thank you to everyone involved in this process, especially @beingkcd for the intro and @kemistry_by_kemi for holding me down 🖤 It’s been a lot, it’s been a journey, we’re tired, but also over the moon with joy and gratitude 🖤

I’m having drinks at Ricks Cage in Casablanca. My live is a movie

Where to begin….I took a wellness retreat to  Marrakech with @_legacyhouse and @mymelaninplus and it was more than I could have ever imagined. 

We stayed at a breathtaking black owned resort @jnanetamsna  Meeting the owner @meryanneinspired was literally seeing what my life could become and I’m forever inspired. 

Our amazing cohosts @michellesaahene and @missmilanzoe did their big one. They were extremely intentional about curating and life changing experience, and did 🙌🏾

I was in Marrakech, then day to trip to Casablanca, then one night in Madrid and no crumbs were left 💅🏾

I was so inspired I decided to plan a sponsored retreat for young women who don’t have the means to travel. Traveling young shows you that’s there’s an entire world to see outside of your city and I wanna give that gift to the younger version of myself. 🥹 

1st: Please visit Africa if you can. This is my second time and it is truly life changing 🙌🏾

2nd: You’re the sum of the 5 ppl you spend the most time with so it is MANDATORY to have a circle of like minded individuals if you want to grow

3rd: LIFE IS SHORT. BOOK THE FLIGHT 🙌🏾

#wellnessretreat #marakech #casablanca #madrid #traveltoafrica
